New Garbage collector in 2.7.8 There is a new parallel garbage collector in SBCL 2.7.8 It is not enabled by default. To enable do a git clone of SBCL and make sure you have version 2.7.8. When compiling use &lsquo;sh make.sh &ndash;without-gencgc &ndash;with-mark-region-gc&rsquo;
Unfortunately after a git fetch I had SBCL 2.3.7.79-556d7db9e which gave the error &lsquo;Feature compatibility check failed, (&quot;:SB-THREAD requires :GENCGC&quot; &hellip;&rsquo;
Anyhow here is a paper announcing the new garbage collector.
